  "text": "Hi, let me tell you about my free time. I work a lot during the week, but I love my weekend. In my free time, I like reading books and I love cooking for my family. On Saturday, I dance at a class near my house. I cannot swim very fast, but I like swimming in the river with my children. In the evening, we watch a movie together and listen to music. My free time is short, but it makes me very happy.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a10_listening_my_free_time.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Good morning, everyone. Let me tell you about my perfect weekend. I have a busy job, so my free time is important to me. On Saturday morning, I love cooking a big breakfast. Then I read the news and listen to music. In the afternoon, I go to the beach with my friends. I like swimming and I love dancing in the evening. On Sunday, I watch a movie at home and rest. I do not like working on the weekend. I like my hobbies too much!",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a10_listening_a_perfect_weekend.mp3"
 },
